580,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:10:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"96fe1a7b9bce38e27861d0c59e8e69a4a8338357","tid":448580,"uid":41610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:29:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Griffith and UTS nursing 聽講都唔錯<br />\n升u個陣唔一定要 ielts 全7，無嘅話好似可以讀英文班代替<br />\n不過grad 之後 register 就一定要有<br />\n<br />\n唔知其他state，不過依家 NSW 所有 public hospital 講到明唔請 international student （請晒 local 先 consider overseas...) , 所以搵工唔易<br />\n<br />\nBTW 唔好簡 Newcastle ....a frd studying nursing there doesn't have a very good experience</blockquote><br />\nNew castle 好似仲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但griffith係queens land <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fa0e8205547c6c822222bf17edf84200807593","tid":448580,"uid":44523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T20:12:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}